languages.text: "Милость в обмен на милость, Ваша Светлость. Не беспокойтесь, послушничество не загубило мои навыки блюстителя".
"I would like to return the favour, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. I assure you, my initiation has not robbed me of my enforcer's skills."

languages.text: « J'aimerais vous rendre la pareille, Votre Seigneurie. Je peux vous assurer que mon initiation n'a en rien amoindri mes talents de prévôt. »
languages.original_text: "I would like to return the favour, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. I assure you, my initiation has not robbed me of my enforcer's skills."

traits.locale_text: « J'aimerais vous rendre la pareille, Votre Seigneurie. Je peux vous assurer que mon initiation n'a en rien amoindri mes talents de prévôt. »

languages.text: «Quisiera devolverle el favor, mi{mf|lord|lady}. Le aseguro que mi iniciación no ha afectado a mis habilidades de agente de seguridad».
languages.original_text: "I would like to return the favour, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. I assure you, my initiation has not robbed me of my enforcer's skills."

traits.locale_text: «Quisiera devolverle el favor, mi{mf|lord|lady}. Le aseguro que mi iniciación no ha afectado a mis habilidades de agente de seguridad».

languages.text: 「ご恩に報いたいと思っているのです、陛下。断言いたしますが、儀式をしても、私のエンフォーサーとしてのスキルは失われてはいません」
languages.original_text: "I would like to return the favour, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. I assure you, my initiation has not robbed me of my enforcer's skills."

traits.locale_text: 「ご恩に報いたいと思っているのです、陛下。断言いたしますが、儀式をしても、私のエンフォーサーとしてのスキルは失われてはいません」

languages.text: “我愿意回报您的好意，大人。我向您保证，尽管我成了神职人员，但我身为执法者的技能并没有变得逊色。”
languages.original_text: "I would like to return the favour, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. I assure you, my initiation has not robbed me of my enforcer's skills."

languages.text: "İyiliğinizin karşılığını vermek isterim {mf|Lord|Leydi} Hazretleri. Sizi temin ederim ki tarikata katılmam, infazcı yeteneklerimden hiçbir şey eksiltmedi."
languages.original_text: "I would like to return the favour, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. I assure you, my initiation has not robbed me of my enforcer's skills."
